<div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Donate & Support Us</h1>
    <p>Your contribution directly supports our conservation projects, empowers our community, and helps protect this vital ecosystem for future generations. Every donation makes a difference.</p>

    <section class="donation-tiers">
        <h2>Choose Your Impact</h2>
        <div class="tiers-grid">
            <div class="tier-card">
                <h3>Wildlife Guardian</h3>
                <h4>$50</h4>
                <p>Funds anti-poaching patrols and provides essential equipment for our rangers.</p>
                <button class="btn-donate-now">Donate Now</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-card">
                <h3>Community Champion</h3>
                <h4>$100</h4>
                <p>Supports a youth training program or helps fund a new community garden project.</p>
                <button class="btn-donate-now">Donate Now</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tier-card">
                <h3>Ecosystem Patron</h3>
                <h4>$250</h4>
                <p>Helps maintain vital water points for wildlife and supports reforestation initiatives.</p>
                <button class="btn-donate-now">Donate Now</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Other Ways to Support</h2>
        <p>Interested in corporate sponsorship or in-kind donations? Please get in touch with our management team via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> to discuss partnership opportunities.</p>
    </section>
</div>

